Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: South Mission Beach
Description: Infamous beach break located in San Diego known for tough crowds, peaky barrels and long lefts.

Name: Hospitals
Description: Whether you want to fish, lobster dive, surf or lounge on the white sands, Hospitals is the spot for you.

Name: Refugio
Description: Decent camping, occasionally fun surf, and a gorgeous stretch of sandy beach.

Name: Manu Bay
Description: Far from home, this surf spot is known as one of the longest left-hand point breaks in the world.

Name: St. Clair
Description: An amazing surf spot located in Dunedin, New Zealand know for its perfect right hand peelers.
